{"word":"G4970 - σφόδρα - sphódra - sfod'-rah - Exceeding","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σφόδρα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sphódra</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sfod'-rah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Exceeding</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மிகவும், மிகுந்த - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"exceedingly, greatly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter plural of <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C6;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2;</b> <b>sphodros</b> (<i>violent</i>; of uncertain derivation) as adverb; <i>vehemently</i>, that is, in <i>a high degree</i>, <i>much:</i> - exceeding (-ly), greatly, sore, very.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}